[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "審査まであと３日。いよいよ大詰めでござる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00765",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "再生数、登録者、どっちもいい感じに増えてるわね。\nこの調子なら審査にも受かるんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00766",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そうも言ってられないかも。『ＱＥジーンズ』も着々と\n人気を獲得してるみたいだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00767",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "むぐぐ……どこまで行ってもライバルってわけね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00768",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "でも、勢いならあなたたちも負けてないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00769",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "その通り！\n３日でこいつらを追い抜くわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00770",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "みんな",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00771",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00772",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00773",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00774",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00775",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00776",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00777",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "お化けでも見るような顔。みんなどうしたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00778",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なんであんたがここに！？\nしれっと交じってんじゃないわよ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00779",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "わああ、ごめんなさい！\nダメだよベップ！　勝手に入っちゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00780",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "不躾な訪問と、ベップの非礼を謝罪。\n申し訳ありません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00781",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "『ＱＥジーンズ』！？　どうしてここに？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00782",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "改めてご挨拶をさせてください。\nはじめまして！　『ＱＥジーンズ』のキューンです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00783",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガ。以後お見知りおきを",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00784",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ベップよ。よろしく",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00785",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "このたびは、皆さんにコラボ動画企画のお誘いに\n参りました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00786",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "コラボ動画……『ＱＥジーンズ』のみんなと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00787",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "はい！　ここ最近皆さんが出されている動画を見て、\nぜひやってみたいなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00788",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "そちらのプロダクションに連絡をしたところ、\n直接本人たちと交渉せよと、ララ社長が",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00789",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "なるほど……ちなみに、どのような内容を\n検討していますでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00790",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "互いに１本ずつ企画を持ち寄ってコラボ動画を\n収録するというものよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00791",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "もちろん、その後はそれぞれのアカウントで\n企画したほうの動画を投稿するわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00792",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まあ、妥当な内容でありまする。\n少し相談しますゆえ、お待ちくだされ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00793",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "まさかこんなことになるなんて……\nねえどうする、鬼門？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00794",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "審査までにもう一手欲しいと思っていたのは事実。\nここはリスクを承知で誘いを受けるべきでありまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00795",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ちょっと、何か裏があるんじゃないの？\nライバルを潰しに来たとか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00796",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ふーむ。それはないと思うでござるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00797",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はあ？　なんでそんなことが言えるわけ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00798",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "それは……まあ良いではありませんか。\n何を仕掛けられたとしても、勝てば良いだけのこと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00799",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "それともヨハナは、自信がないでござるか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00800",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はっ、そんなわけないでしょ。望むところよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00801",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "では、答えは決まりでござるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00802",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "お待たせいたした、『ＱＥジーンズ』の皆様方",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00803",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者たち『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』は\nそのお誘いを受けまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00804",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]